
<form action="<url>" method="<tipi i metodes>">
    <input 1>
    <input 2>
    ...
    <input type="submit">
</form>

GET -> nese duam te marrim nje resource nga serveri
POST -> nese duam te "udhezojme" serverin te ndryshoje gjendjen
    (p.sh.: krijimi i nje objekti te ri ne databaze)

Request (Client-Server):
	POST / HTTP/1.1
	Host: www.example.com

	<verb> <relative-path (URI)> <specification>
	Host: <plaintext>

	Verbs: GET POST PUT DELETE OPTIONS HEAD ...

    <body>
        <form action="<url>" method="POST">
            <input 1>
            <input 2>
            ...
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
    </body>